WiFi & BT Module
----------------

The default |product| without the CM5 does not include a Wi-Fi/BT module. |br|
If you include a CM5 that has the Wi-Fi/BT module, the product will have Wi-Fi/BT feature.
The product also has an SMA connector for an external WiFi/BT antenna:

.. rst-class:: text-center

   |wifi_img|

   *WiFi+BT Antenna*

.. attention::

    The product does not come shipped with the Wi-Fi/BT module by default.

:pagebreak:`True`
